	~RASharCM 14 3 3 3 12 3~
	~RASharCM 0 0 0 0 0 0~
	~RASharCM 14 3 3 3 12 3~
    ~RASharCM 14 3 3 3 12 3~
	~RASharCM 0 0 0 0 0 1 0 0 0~
	~RASharCM 1 1 1 1 1 1~
	~DeitiesOfFaerun\Tables\RASharCM.2da~
	~K_CM_H   K_CM_HE   K_CM_E   K_CM_G   K_CM_HO   K_CM_HL   K_CM_D~
	~0x04000000 14~
